      • fillTheHashMap

        public void fillTheHashMap(java.lang.String timescale)
        Overloaded method with restriction of given timesclace. Fill HashMap only with values which meet the conditions of given timeScale This method only works for given year and quarter. It should have 2 timeScales from and to and own comparator for better results now it only for one year and one quarter and only if its correctly written. This should be solved with UI. For example slider. setting keyOrder for default order of Vendors in HashMap
